snippet.title: Morning Star Teaser Trailer - E3 2018
snippet.description:
A game by Metkis

http://morningstarthegame.com

Morning Star is a first-person farming game set in a post-cyberpunk world where computers are your soil and software is your seeds.

CREDITS
Trailer by Metkis and Lilia Mirkhabutdinova-Martin
Music and Sound by Gordon McGladdery and A Shell in the Pit
